What is an ROV Manipulator Arm?
ROV manipulator arms are specialized robotic systems mounted on remotely operated underwater vehicles designed for precision tasks like gripping, cutting, and equipment maintenance in deep-sea environments. These sophisticated arms feature high-pressure resistance, multi-axis articulation, and advanced control systems that enable complex underwater operations across multiple industries.

