Perform precision underwater welding with minimal human oversight
Conduct scientific sampling with millimeter accuracy
Execute complex tasks through predictive movement algorithms
The market for these intelligent systems is projected to grow at 18.4% CAGR through 2030, creating lucrative opportunities for innovators at the intersection of robotics and artificial intelligence.

